OL,3,CLindsey Burrow: Who Cares For Our
OL,4,CCarers?
OL,6,FUnpaid carers in England and Wales are
OL,7,Fproviding care worth an estimated #162
OL,8,Fbillion a year, the equivalent of a
OL,9,Fsecond NHS. But what is the cost to
OL,10,Fthose who take on the responsibility
OL,11,Fof caring for others? Lindsey Burrow,
OL,12,Fwho is an unpaid carer for her former
OL,13,Frugby league player husband Rob, has
OL,14,Fbeen finding out.
