OL,3,CLindsey Burrow: Who Cares For Our
OL,4,CCarers?
OL,6,FThe government told Tonight: "Unpaid
OL,7,Fcarers play a vital role which is why
OL,8,Fwe've increased Carer's Allowance by
OL,9,Falmost #1200 since 2010. Carers may
OL,10,Falso be eligible for financial support
OL,11,Fthrough Universal Credit. Local
OL,12,Fauthorities are responsible for
OL,13,Fassessing unpaid carers in their area
OL,14,Fand we've earmarked #327 million
OL,15,Fthrough our Better Care Fund this year
OL,16,Fproviding carers with advice, support,
OL,17,Fshort breaks and respite services."
