OL,3,CLindsey Burrow: Who Cares For Our
OL,4,CCarers?
OL,6,FIn a poll of 2,000 people,
OL,7,Fcommissioned by Tonight, nearly three
OL,8,Fquarters of those who took part said
OL,9,Funpaid carers are underappreciated in
OL,10,Fthe UK. What's more, 66% of those
OL,11,Fasked said that the Government is
OL,12,Fdoing a bad job at supporting unpaid
OL,13,Fcarers. What do you think?
